@startuml
title Object lifecycle: Access token
[*] --> NotIssued
NotIssued --> Rejected : credential invalid or account inactive
NotIssued --> Issued : login succeeds
Issued --> Accepted : authenticated request passes JWT strategy
Accepted --> Accepted : subsequent authenticated request
Issued --> Expired : expires_at reached
Accepted --> Expired : expires_at reached
Rejected --> [*]
Expired --> [*]
Accepted --> [*]
@enduml
